and the South Korean puppets for frequently staging reckless 
military exercises and committing provocations against the 
Democratic People's Republic of Korea. 
  Entering May, the South Korean puppets have staged 
large-scale manoeuvres socalled "combined tactical exercises for 
the first half of the year" involving the three services in an 
area near the military demarcation line (MDL). They have also 
reinforced Armed Forces and fired bullets and shells there, 
perpetrating military provocations almost every day. 
  The information bitterly denounces these moves of the U.S. 
imperialists and the South Korean puppets as an intolerable 
crime challenging pointblank the desire and efforts of the 
Korean nation to avert the danger of a nuclear war and open a 
new phase of the peace and peaceful reunification of the country. 
