against the North they had worked out together with the United 
States, and have massively introduced latest-type combat 
equipment from the U.S. they have also massed the puppet Armed 
Forces in areas near the MDL and committed military 
provocations, threatening "a tough counteraction" and 
"retaliation" against the North. This indicates that their 
belligerent moves have reached a very dangerous stage. 
  We want peace. But we are not afraid of war. The U.S. 
imperialists and the South Korean puppets had better act with 
discretion, clearly mindful that if they dare ignite another 
war, they would have to pay dearly for it. 

