They were Secretary Nieves Confesor said Captain Ali bin 
(Mayad) at [word indistinct] immigration did not allow the team 
of five Filipinos to proceed for security reasons. [sentence as 
heard] Confesor said the mission was assured that every Filipino 
evacuee found crossing the border will be given assistance and 
turned over to the team at the Al-Hyatt Hotel in (Qizan). 

