<H4>    Route `Completely' Cut Off </H4>

<F P=102> BK1605023794 (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union 
Front of Cambodia in Cambodian 2330 GMT 15 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK1605023794 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union 
